How to add SSH key in Secure CRT?
Generating your key with SecureCRT:
Start SecureCRT.
Under the Tools menu, select Create Public Key.
This will open the Key Generation Wizard. ...
In the Key type dropdown, select RSA and click Next.
Enter a strong passphrase in the Passphrase box and then enter it again in the Confirm Passphrase box. ...
Enter the key length.
